title: 2021 South Region wrestling: Final results (Reg. 7 & 8)
body: NJSIAA South Region Wrestling Championships, April 17, 2021The best high school boys wrestlers in New Jersey open pursuit of state titles on Saturday with the opening round of the NJSIAA/Rothman Orthopaedics wrestling tournament.The South Jersey Region tournament is set for Cherry Hill East High School.Complete results are on the way from , so stay tuned.The results for the final round:2-, St. Augustine d. 1-, Kingsway, 3-2.2-, Southern d. 1-, Eastern, 1-0.2-, Kingsway d. 5-, Camden Catholic, 5-2.1-, Washington Township d. 2-, Cinnaminson, 5-4 (UTB).1-, Clearview d. 2-, Southern, 15-0 (TF 4:18).1-, Southern p. 6-, Camden Catholic, 3:07.1-, Woodstown d. 2-, Toms River East, 3-2.Note to readers: if you purchase something through one of our affiliate links we may earn a commission.
